N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1935.1 - Demonstration aspects

State Regulations

The corporation may request assistance of eligible
applicants in preparing and compiling findings related to the development of
projects. Such information will be utilized in assessing the effectiveness of
certain projects and in reports to the Legislature. Notes
